---
// Problem section - Why solo habit apps fail
---

<section class="problem section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="problem-content reveal">
      <span class="label label-coral">The Real Problem</span>
      <h2>You don't fail because you lack <em>tools</em>. You fail because you're <em>alone</em>.</h2>

      <div class="problem-grid">
        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
              <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-text">
            <h3>Reminders you ignore</h3>
            <p>Notifications become noise. There is no consequence for swiping them away.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 2v4m0 12v4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83m8.48 8.48l2.83 2.83M2 12h4m12 0h4M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83m8.48-8.48l2.83-2.83"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-text">
            <h3>Streaks nobody sees</h3>
            <p>Breaking a private streak costs nothing. There is no social weight to letting yourself down.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"></path>
              <path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-text">
            <h3>Easy to skip</h3>
            <p>When the only person you let down is yourself, skipping becomes painless.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="problem-item">
          <div class="problem-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <path d="M16 16s-1.5-2-4-2-4 2-4 2"></path>
              <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="9.01" y2="9"></line>
              <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="15.01" y2="9"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="problem-text">
            <h3>Goals that fade</h3>
            <p>Without external accountability, motivation fades after the first week.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-solution reveal">
      <div class="solution-arrow">
        <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--coral)" stroke-width="2">
          <line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"></line>
          <polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <p class="solution-intro">TinyAct changes the equation:</p>
      <h3 class="solution-statement">
        When your partner's streak depends on you, <span class="text-gradient">skipping is not an option.</span>
      </h3>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .problem-content {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .problem-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: var(--space-6) auto var(--space-12);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .problem-content h2 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .problem-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    text-align: left;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: all var(--transition-slow);
  }

  .problem-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .problem-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .problem-text h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .problem-text p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .problem-solution {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: var(--space-8);
  }

  .solution-arrow {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
    50% { transform: translateY(8px); }
  }

  .solution-intro {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .solution-statement {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: var(--leading-snug);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .problem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
